# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values. **Never commit `.env` to version control.**

```env
# GitHub Personal Access Token (read-only, for auto-updater to fetch private release assets)
# Required only if you host releases on a private GitHub repo.
GH_TOKEN=your_github_pat_here

# Optional: override the GitHub owner/repo for auto-updates (defaults set in electron/main.js)
GITHUB_OWNER=your-github-username
GITHUB_REPO=newsen
```
